{"timestamp": "2025-12-05 13:32:39.496610", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission recorded.\n\nSummary of submission:\n- is_anomaly: true\n- faulty_devices: [\"host_2_1_1_1\"]\n- root_cause_name: [\"host_missing_ip\"]\n\nSuggested immediate remediation (not required for submission):\n- Assign a valid IPv4 address to host_2_1_1_1 (either via DHCP or correct static config). Verify with: ip addr show eth0 and ip route.\n- If using DHCP: check DHCP client logs on the host and DHCP server lease table; verify switch VLAN/port and DHCP relay configuration if leases are not granted.\n- After assigning IP, verify connectivity: ping 10.200.0.2 and confirm DNS resolution and reachability to web servers.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2204, "output_tokens": 151, "total_tokens": 2355, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 1664}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
